name: Recycled Organic Chick Pea Bag
description: Recycled organic Chick Pea sack. Now a handy bag. Two compartments and very organic. Measuring 40cm by 30 cm.

name: Save the ocean pouf
description:
Do something other than throw all your plastic waste in the rubbish. 
  Out door or indoor seat. Made from sail cloth, a foam insert on top (inside) to keep it soft, and personalised with a letter or logo.  The bottom is made from a sturdy mesh and a zipper so you can just keep filling it with plastic packaging, bubble wrap and plastic bags.

name: Sail cloth hand bag
description: This style has been a favourite for a while now.Two internal pockets, 25mm grey webbing strap at 1.05m long. The blue 3di sail main body is part of a sail that raced around the world 2011-12.  The white strip will glow in the dark if it has seen some daylight during the day. The circular ends are built from a cuben fibre down wind sail that sailed in the same race. A marine grade size 10 zipper and sewn together with 138 sailmaking thread. The bag itself is 300mm long x 140mm diameter. Plenty of room for a few goodies.

name: Sail handbag.
description: Super rare super light and super strong pink cuben fibre ladies handbag measures 38cm across the top and is 20 cm at the deepest point and 10cm wide. It has four internal pockets and a rope handle that works over the shoulder or can be doubled up to carry in the hand. The rope handles are spliced on so there are no big knots to deal with. It is built from a tinted pink cuben fibre  sail that has raced around the world in 2008-09 and closes with a size 10 marine grade chunky zipper. All sewing is done with size 138 sail making thread.

name: Handmade sailcloth handbag
description: This style has been a favourite for a while now.Two internal pockets, 25mm black webbing strap at 1.05m long. The red kevlar body is part of a sail that raced around the world 2006. A marine grade zipper and sewn together with 138 sailmaking thread. The bag itself is 300mm long x 140mm diameter. Plenty of room for a few goodies.

name: Recycled sail Travel Bag
description:
Large light weight travel bag. 60cm x 27cm (base) and 30cm high in the middle. Built mostly from a carbon-kevlar sail that once sailed in Valencia in the Americas' cup 2007 with a sturdy sail bag cloth base.50mm black webbing handles that work in the hand or carry your luggage like a back pack over the shoulders.
Sewn with 138 sail making thread and double zipper sliders on a marine grade zipper.

name: Recycled messenger bag
description:
A combination of materials used here but for the most part it is built from a carbon-kevlar sail that was used in the Americas' cup 2007. Although the boats and the sails from this era are not much good for anything now the old sails still make good bags.
 Strong, light weight and just a little bit cool. Perfect for the lap top. (padded bottom, two layers of bubble wrap). 
26cm high, 35cm across and 8cm deep. Adjustable 50mm black seat belt webbing strap.

name: Sail cloth key ring
description: Red kevlar sail cloth key ring loop. Over you wrist or on the handle bars. An easy way to keep track of the keys and have your hands free.

name: Recycled sail-shopping bag
description:
This bag is ideal for shopping or taking to the beach. Carry in the hand or over the shoulder.  
  Built by a sailmaker it has 6 internal pockets and a marine grade  zipper closing. The blue part of the bag is built from sail bag cloth left on the loft floor during production of sail bags built for a boat competing in 2011-2012 round the world race. The upper portion of the bag is built from part of a cuben fibre down wind sail that has also raced around the world
 The handles are 25mm grey webbing (300mm high) and the entire bag is sewn together with 138 marine grade thread.
The size is 21cm x 12cm (base) and 37cm high.

name: Messenger/Laptop bag

Measuring 26cm high, 35cm across and 8cm deep. Adjustable 50mm blue seat belt webbing strap. Built from a 3di sail that raced around the world in the volvo race 2011-12.

description: This ladies handbag measures 38cm across the top and is 20 cm at the deepest point.
